\id 1TH ‑ Ikizu 1 Thessalonians 
\h 1 Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\toc3 1 Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\toc2 1 Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\toc1 Ɨnyarʉbha ye embere ya Paaurʉ kwa Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\mt2 Ɨnyarʉbha ye embere ya Paaurʉ kwa 
\mt1 Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\imt1 Ʉbhʉkangati 
\ip Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ yandikirwɨ nu umutumwa Paaurʉ hamwɨmwɨ na Sirwanʉ na Timoseo. Paaurʉ aarɨ ahikiirɨ mʉrʉbhɨri ʉrʉkʉrʉ rwi icharʉ cha Makɨdʉniya, ribhaga ryo orogendo rwazɨ rwa kabhɨrɨ rwu ukurwaza Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu igʉrʉ wa Yɨɨsu (\xt Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 17:1‑10\xt*). Mʉrʉbhɨri muyo abhaatʉ bha teemwa zʉʉsi bhakiisirirya ɨngʼana yaazɨ. Hanʉ Paaurʉ iimiiriiryɨ risengerero Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ hayo, ɨnyaakʉ haari ɨkatanga kʉbhabhona abhiisirirya. Ɨnyaakʉ yiyo yaarɨ ɨrakorwa na Abhayaahudi. Paaurʉ akatɨnɨra kʉbhʉʉka rogendo rʉmwɨ. 
\ip Hanʉ aaruurɨ iyo, akamara ibhaga isuuhu, akatʉma Timoseo, ajɨ Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ kʉbhaha umwʉyʉ abhiisirirya bhi iyo. Paaurʉ umwene atagiirɨyʉ, akangʼeha kurwaza zɨmbaara ɨzɨndɨ. Timoseo akagarʉka kwa Paaurʉ, akamuhirɨra amangʼana igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya nu ubhwikari bhwa abhiisirirya bha Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ. Hanʉ Paaurʉ iigwirɨ amangʼana gayo, akazomerwa bhʉkʉngʼu, akabhaandɨkɨra ɨnyarʉbha yʉ ʉkʉbhakumya ku ubhwisirirya nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwabhʉ. Akabhabhʉʉrɨra ɨkɨ kɨrabhoneka kʉBhakiriisitʉ hanʉ bhakukwa na ribhaga rɨnʉ Yɨɨsu akʉgarʉka kʉʉsɨ. Akabhaha umwʉyʉ korereke bhangʼehe kwikara ubhwikari bhʉnʉ bhokozomera Mungu. 
\c 1  
\s1 Amakeerenʼya 
\p  
\v 1 Ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ nandikirɨ inyɨ Paaurʉ, hamwɨmwɨ na Sirwanʉ\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Sirwanʉ \ft arabhirikirwa \fqa Siira \ft mʉkɨtabhʉ cha Amahocha ga Abhatumwa.\f* na Timoseo. Tʉrabhaandɨkɨra imwɨ abhiisirirya bhʉ ʉrʉbhɨri rwa Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ, mwiribhita rya abhaatʉ bhanʉ mwisiriiryɨ Bhaabha Mungu nʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ. 
\p Ɨbhɨgʉngi no omorembe bhɨbhɨ na niimwɨ. 
\s1 Ubhwisirirya bhwa Abhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\p  
\v 2 Tʉramukumya Mungu ribhaga ryʉsi igʉrʉ waanyu bhʉʉsi, na tʉrabhasabhɨra tʉtakuniha.  
\v 3 Hanʉ tʉkʉbhasabhɨra kwa Bhaabha wɨɨtʉ Mungu, tʉragihiita mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwazɨ emeremo gɨnʉ mokokora kubhwisirirya. Tʉraguhiita umucha gwanyu gʉnʉ gukurwɨra kʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwanyu, na chɨmbu mwimiiriirɨ kurwa ku ubhwisɨgi bhwanyu kʉMʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ. 
\p  
\v 4 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ imwɨ, bhanʉ Mungu asɨɨgirɨ, twɨzɨ Mungu abharʉbhwɨrɨ kʉbha abhaatʉ bhaazɨ.  
\v 5 Tʉmɨnyirɨbhu kʉ kʉbha hanʉ twarwazirɨ kwa niimwɨ Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu, tʉtaarwazirɨ kwa amangʼana ageenebhu. Nawe tʉkarwaza kwa amanaga na kwe Ekoro Ɨndɨndu,\f + \fr 1:5 \fk Ekoro Ɨndɨndu\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* na tono obhoheene kʉbha ɨngʼana yiyo nɨ‑ya amaheene. Imwɨ mwɨzɨ bhwaheene chɨmbu twarɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ, korereke tʉbhasakiryɨ.  
\v 6 Nangabha mʉkanyaakibhwa bhʉkʉngʼu kʉ kʉbha yu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu, mʉkasʉngʼaana ɨngʼana yiyo kobhozomerwa bhʉnʉ bhukurwa kwe Ekoro Ɨndɨndu. Chɨmbu mwakʉrirɨbhu, mʉkɨɨga ekerenjo chɨtʉ ne ekerenjo chʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 7 Kwɨbhu, mʉbhɨɨrɨ ekerenjo kɨzʉmu kubhiisirirya bhʉʉsi bhanʉ bharɨ mucharʉ cha Makɨdʉniya na cha Akaaya.  
\v 8 Abhaatʉ bhiigwirɨ kurwa kwa niimwɨ ɨngʼana yʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ. Ɨtarɨ kʉbhaatʉ bha Makɨdʉniya na bha Akaaya abheene, nawe ubhwisirirya bhwanyu kwa Mungu, bhʉmɨnyɨkɨɨnɨ hʉʉsi. Kʉgayo tʉtakwinyaacha kʉgamba chʉchʉsi igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu.  
\v 9 Hanʉ hʉʉsi tukuja, abhaatʉ bharagamba bhwaheene igʉrʉ we eteemwa yanyu, chɨmbu mwatʉsʉngʼaanirɨ hanʉ twizirɨ kwa niimwɨ. Bharamenyeekererya chɨmbu mwatigirɨ amasambwa gaanyu na kwichʉrɨra Mungu, korereke momohokerye ewe ʉmʉhʉru na wa amaheene,  
\v 10 na kʉrɨnda Umwana waazɨ\f + \fr 1:10 \fk Umwana waazɨ\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it Umwana wa Mungu\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* Yɨɨsu kurwa mwisaarʉ. Ewe newe Mungu akamuryʉra, na newe akʉtʉsabhʉra mʉtɨnɨrʉ ya Mungu yɨnʉ ikuuza. 
\c 2  
\s1 Emeremo ja Paaurʉ na abhakɨndichazɨ Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\p  
\v 1 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ imwɨ, imubheene mwɨzɨ ukuuza kwɨtʉ kwa niimwɨ kʉtaarɨ kwa bhʉʉha.  
\v 2 Kwikɨ mwɨzɨ hanʉ twarɨ tʉkɨɨrɨ kuhika kwa niimwɨ, tʉkanyaakibhwa na kutukwa mʉrʉbhɨri rwa Firipi. Nangabha kwarɨ nʉ ʉbhʉkʉngʼu kwa niimwɨ, nawe Mungu akatoha ʉbhʉnaja bhu ukwerekeererya Ɨngʼana yaazɨ Ɨnzʉmu.  
\v 3 Amangʼana ganʉ tʉkʉkandikija kwa niimwɨ gatarɨ ga rʉrɨmɨ, hamwɨ kwa ngʼeera, nʉʉrʉ kʉbhakangirirya. 
\p  
\v 4 Nawe toreerekeererya kʉ kʉbha Mungu akatwisirirya, akatoha emeremo ju ukwerekeererya Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu. Tʉtakwiseega kozomera abhaatʉ, nawe toreenda kozomera Mungu, wʉnʉ ahaarora gʉʉsi ganʉ garɨ mozekoro za abhaatʉ.  
\v 5 Mwɨzɨ twarɨ tʉtakʉgamba amangʼana korereke mʉtʉsɨɨgɨ, na Mungu, nɨ‑mʉmɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri kʉbha tʉtakʉgamba amangʼana ganʉ gatarɨ ga amaheene, korereke tobhone ubhwera.  
\v 6 Na twarɨ tʉtakomohya bhukumuka kʉbhaatʉ, kurwa kwa niimwɨ, nʉʉrʉ kurwa kʉbhandɨ bhʉbhʉʉsi. 
\p Twarɨ tʉratʉra kwenda ebhegero obhorebhe kurwa kwa niimwɨ, kʉ kʉbha itwɨ, nɨ‑bhatumwa\f + \fr 2:6 \fk Abhatumwa\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* bha Kiriisitʉ, nawe tʉtakʉrirɨbhu.  
\v 7 Twarɨ bhanyʉʉhu kwa niimwɨ nchʉ ʉmʉkari akorera abhaana bhaazɨ.  
\v 8 Tʉkabhasɨɨga imwɨ bhʉkʉngʼu necho kiyo tʉkazomerwa, ɨtarɨ kʉbhabhʉʉrɨra Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu kurwa kwa Mungu iyeene, nawe nu ukwihurucha kwɨtʉ kokora gʉʉsi ganʉ gakwenderwa kʉbhasakirya. Tʉkakorabhu kʉ kʉbha imwɨ mʉbhɨɨrɨ bhasɨɨgwa bhɨɨtʉ. 
\p  
\v 9 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, mʉrahiita umucha gwɨtʉ nʉ ʉkʉnyaaka kwɨtʉ, twarɨ tʉrakora emeremo ubhutikʉ nu umwise. Twarɨ tʉrakorabhu, korereke hanʉ tukurwaza Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu kurwa kwa Mungu, tʉtaaza kʉnyaacha ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi kwa niimwɨ.  
\v 10 Imwɨ nɨ‑bhamɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri bhɨɨtʉ, na Mungu wʉʉsi, nɨ‑mʉmɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri, eteemwa yɨɨtʉ kwa niimwɨ abhiisirirya, yaarɨ nzʉmu na ya amaheene, ɨtaatɨmirwɨ isoro.  
\v 11 Na mwɨzɨ hanʉ twarɨ kwa niimwɨ twarɨ tʉrabhakorera bhʉʉsi chɨmbu bhaabha akʉbhakorera abhaana bhaazɨ. Twarɨ tʉrabhaha umwʉyʉ na kubhiibhisirirya na kubhiisasaama,  
\v 12 korereke mwikarɨ chɨmbu Mungu asɨɨgirɨ. Mungu newe abhabhirikiirɨ korereke musikɨrɨ mʉbhʉtɨmi na mʉbhʉgʉngʉ bhwazɨ. 
\p  
\v 13 Naatu tʉna ringʼana ɨrɨndɨ ryu ukukumya Mungu tʉtaana kiniha, kʉ kʉbha hanʉ mwitɨgɨɨrɨɨrɨ ɨngʼana yaazɨ kurwa kwa niitwɨ, mʉtaayɨsʉngʼaanirɨ ncha ringʼana rya abhaatʉ. Nawe mʉkayɨsʉngʼaana nchɨ ɨngʼana kurwa kwa Mungu, na amaheene nɨmbu ɨrɨ. Ɨngʼana yiyo ɨrakora emeremo mumyʉyʉ janyu, imwɨ bhanʉ mumwisiriiryɨ.  
\v 14 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, ganʉ gaabhabhwɨnɨ abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakwisirirya Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ mʉmasengerero ga Mungu ganʉ gari mucharʉ cha Yudeya, nego na niimwɨ gaabhabhwɨnɨ. Abhaatʉ bhaanyu bhakabhanyaacha, chɨmbu Abhayaahudi abhakɨndichabhʉ bhaabhanyaakiryɨ.  
\v 15 Abhayaahudi bhayo, nebho bhiitirɨ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu na abharʉʉtɨrɨri bhɨ ɨkarɨ. Na nebho bhaatʉnyaakiryɨ itwɨ. Abhaatʉ bhayo, bhariigatanʼya Mungu na bhatakwigwana na abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi,  
\v 16 kʉ kʉbha bharatorecha kurwaza Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu kʉbhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatarɨ Abhayaahudi. Bharaanga abhaatʉ bhatasabhurwa. Nɨmbu bhakʉkaja kuhicha ʉbhʉbhɨ bhwabhʉ bhʉnʉ bhakokora ibhaga ryʉsi. Nawe ʉbhʉrʉrʉ bhwa Mungu bhʉbhahikiirɨ! 
\s1 Paaurʉ na abhakɨndichazɨ bhariigomba kuhunana na Abhatɨsarʉʉniki 
\p  
\v 17 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, ʉkʉtaana kwɨtʉ na niimwɨ kwarɨ kwibhaga isuuhubhu, nʉ ʉkʉtaana kuyo kwarɨ kwa mʉbhɨrɨ, kʉtarɨ kwe ekoro. Na kwa ribhaga riyo ryʉsi, twarɨ turiigomba tuhunanɨ.  
\v 18 Neho tokeenda tuuzɨ kwa niimwɨ, kɨnda inyɨ Paaurʉ naarɨ nereenda kuuza manga kaaru, nawe Shɨtaani\f + \fr 2:18 \fk Shɨtaani\ft . Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* akatorecha.  
\v 19 Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu hanʉ akuuza, nɨ‑bha wɨɨwɨ bhanʉ bharaabhɨ ɨtangɨ yu ubhwisɨgi bhwɨtʉ? Na nɨ‑bha wɨɨwɨ bhanʉ bharaabhɨ ʉbhʉtangɨ bhwo obhozomerwa nɨ ɨkɨrʉngʉ chɨtʉ chu ubhuhizi? Mʉtarɨ imwɨ?  
\v 20 Maheene, imwɨ niimwɨ bhanʉ mʉraagiryɨ twiheeme no okozomerwa. 
\c 3  
\s1 Paaurʉ aratʉma Timoseo Tɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\p  
\v 1 Ɨtɨnɨrʉ tʉkatamwa kwigumirirya, kʉ kʉbha tʉtaamɨnyirɨ ganʉ gakokorwa iyo. Neho tʉkarora, itwɨ tʉsaagɨ itubheene mʉrʉbhɨri rwa Asɨnɨ,  
\v 2 tʉtʉmɨ Timoseo umuhiiri wɨɨtʉ, korereke aazɨ abhanajɨ na kʉbhaha umwʉyʉ mubhwisirirya bhwanyu. Ewe, ne‑mohocha mʉkɨndichɨtʉ wa Mungu, ku kwerekeererya Ɨngʼana Ɨnzʉmu igʉrʉ wa Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 3 Tʉkakorabhu korereke ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi mʉbhaniimwɨ atakwa umwʉyʉ kʉ kʉbha yɨ ɨnyaakʉ yɨnʉ. Imwɨ mwɨzɨ, toreenderwa kʉhɨtɨra ɨnyaakʉ.  
\v 4 Mwɨzɨ gayo, kʉ kʉbha hanʉ twarɨ na niimwɨ, twarɨ tʉrabhuurirwa kʉbha tʉranyaakibhwa. Nangʉ nɨmbu gaabhɨɨrɨ. 
\p  
\v 5 Kiyo necho kigiriryɨ nɨkatamwa kwigumirirya, nɨkatʉma Timoseo kwa niimwɨ, korereke nemenye amangʼana gu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu. Nɨkakorabhu kwa kwiseega kʉbha hamwɨ Shɨtaani abhagɨmirɨ na kʉbharimirya, ne emeremo jʉsi gɨnʉ twakʉrirɨ kwa niimwɨ gɨbhɨ ja bhʉʉha. 
\s1 Amangʼana amazʉmu kurwa kʉBhatɨsarʉʉnikɨ 
\p  
\v 6 Nangʉ Timoseo agarukirɨ kurwa kwa niimwɨ, atubhuuriirɨ amangʼana amazʉmu igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwanyu. Atubhuuriirɨ mʉratuhiita bhwaheene kɨrakabhu, na mʉbhɨɨrɨ na amɨɨga gu ukurumana na niitwɨ, chɨmbu itwʉsi tʉbhɨɨrɨ nɨ ɨnamba kurumana na niimwɨ. 
\p  
\v 7 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, ɨngʼana igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu, ɨtʉkʉngʉʉrirɨ imyʉyʉ mʉnyaakʉ yɨɨtʉ yʉʉsi.  
\v 8 Nangʉ tʉrahezera, kʉ kʉbha imwɨ mwimiiriirɨ bhwɨma kʉMʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 9 Nangʉ tʉrarɨhakɨ Mungu igʉrʉ wu ubhwisirirya bhwanyu? Tʉratʉra kumukumyabhwɨ kobhozomerwa ʉbhʉkʉrʉ bhʉnʉ tʉnabhwɨ mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwazɨ igʉrʉ waanyu?  
\v 10 Tʉrasabha Mungu kumucha ubhutikʉ nu umwise, atʉsakiryɨ tujɨ kwikɨ kwa niimwɨ, korereke tʉbhasakiryɨ kɨnʉ musuuhiirwɨ kubhwisirirya bhwanyu. 
\p  
\v 11 Tʉrasabha Bhaabha wɨɨtʉ Mungu umwene, nʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu, atokorere ɨnzɨra yu ukuuza kwa niimwɨ.  
\v 12 Ʉmʉkʉrʉ abhoongere ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwʉ ʉkʉsɨɨgana imubheene kobheene na kʉbhasɨɨga abhandɨ bhʉʉsi, chɨmbu itwɨ tʉbhasɨɨgirɨ imwɨ.  
\v 13 Na abhanajɨ imyʉyʉ janyu, korereke mʉbhɨ abhaatʉ abharɨndu, mʉtaana isoro mʉbhʉtangɨ bhwa Bhaabha Mungu, ribhaga rɨnʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu araazɨ hamwɨmwɨ na abharɨndu bhaazɨ bhʉʉsi.\f + \fr 3:13 \fk Abharɨndu bhaazɨ bhʉʉsi\ft , ʉbhʉgaruri ʉbhʉndɨ bhʉratʉra kʉbha, \fqa bhamaraika bhaazɨ bhʉʉsi. \ft Kʉmaragɨrɨra bhʉkʉngʼu, rora ringʼana \ft \+it abharɨndu\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* 
\c 4  
\s1 Eteemwa yɨnʉ Mungu asɨɨgirɨ 
\p  
\v 1 Nangʉ abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, mwigirɨ kurwa kwa niitwɨ chɨmbu ikwenderwa kwikara, korereke komozomerya Mungu. Maheene nɨmbu mukwikara. Nangʉ, tʉrabhasabha na kubhiisasaama kʉbhʉnaja bhwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu, mʉkajɨ kokorabhu na kʉkɨraho.  
\v 2 Mwɨzɨ bhwaheene ganʉ twabhaswajiryɨ kʉbhʉnaja bhwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu. 
\p  
\v 3 Mungu areenda mʉbhɨ abhaatʉ abharɨndu, mutiisikirya kokora ɨtaarʉ.  
\v 4 Imubhʉʉsi muhizɨ ɨmɨbhɨrɨ janyu, mʉbhʉrɨndu na kwisʉʉka.  
\v 5 Mʉtabha nɨ ɨnamba mbɨ ncha abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatɨɨzɨ Mungu.  
\v 6 Mʉgayo, ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi atasariirya ʉmʉkɨndichazɨ, nʉʉrʉ kʉmʉkangirirya. Tʉmarirɨ kʉbhabhʉʉrɨra na kʉbharecha, bhʉʉsi bhanʉ bhakokora gayo, Ʉmʉkʉrʉ newe akʉrɨhanʼya isiirɨ ya gayo gʉʉsi.  
\v 7 Mungu ataatubhirikiirɨ kokora ɨtaarʉ, nawe akatʉbhɨrɨkɨra twikarɨ mʉbhʉrɨndu.  
\v 8 Mmbe, ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi wʉnʉ akwanga amiija gayo, atakumwanga ʉmʉʉtʉ, nawe araanga Mungu, wʉnʉ akʉbhaha imwɨ Ekoro yaazɨ Ɨndɨndu. 
\p  
\v 9 Nangʉ, ɨtakwenderwa tʉbhaandɨkɨrɨ imwɨ igʉrʉ wʉ ʉkʉsɨɨgana, kʉ kʉbha imwɨ imubheene mwijibhwɨ na Mungu kʉsɨɨgana.  
\v 10 Maheene, mʉbhɨɨrɨ mʉrabhakorerabhu abhakɨndichanyu bhʉʉsi bhanʉ bhari mucharʉ cha Makɨdʉniya. Nangʉ tʉrabhasabha, abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, mʉkajɨ kʉsɨɨganabhu na kʉkɨraho. 
\p  
\v 11 Mʉbhɨ nu umwʉyʉ gu ukwikara ubhwikari bhwo omorembe. Ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi atiisikirya mʉmangʼana ga abhandɨ, nawe akore emeremo jazɨ umwene, chɨmbu twabhaswajiryɨ.  
\v 12 Hayo mʉrabha mwɨrɨkɨɨnʼyɨ eteemwa ɨnzʉmu kʉbhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatarɨ Abhakiriisitʉ. Naatu mʉtakʉbha abhaatʉ bhu ukwisega bhya abhandɨ. 
\s1 Ukuryʉka kwa abhaku urusikʉ rwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu 
\p  
\v 13 Nawe abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, toreenda momenye amangʼana ga bhanʉ bhakuurɨ, korereke mutigɨ kurumɨka ncha abhaatʉ abhandɨ bhanʉ bhataana ubhwisɨgi bhwu ukuryʉka.  
\v 14 Itwɨ, tʉmɨnyirɨ Yɨɨsu akakwa nu ukuryʉka. Kuriyo, turiisega Mungu arabharyʉra na kʉbhareeta hamwɨmwɨ na Yɨɨsu bhʉʉsi bhanʉ bhaakuurɨ bhamwisiriiryɨ. 
\p  
\v 15 Mmbe, ganʉ tʉkʉbhabhʉʉrɨra ni‑miija gʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu, kʉbha itwɨ bhanʉ tʉkʉbha bhahʉru hanʉ ewe akʉgarʉka, tʉtakʉbhakangatɨra abhaku kuhunana neewe.  
\v 16 Ʉmʉkʉrʉ umwene ariika kurwa mwisaarʉ. Aragamba kwiraka ikʉrʉ, maraika ʉmʉkʉrʉ wʉʉsi arabhɨrɨkɨra kwiraka na rihembe rya Mungu rɨrabhɨrɨkɨra. Neho bhanʉ bhaakuurɨ bhiisiriiryɨ Kiriisitʉ, bharakangata kuryukuribhwa.  
\v 17 Akʉmara itwɨ abhahʉru, bhanʉ tʉsaagirɨ, tʉrasakurwa hamwɨmwɨ nabhʉ mʉmasaarʉ, korereke tʉmʉsʉngʼaanɨ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ mwisaarʉ. Neho tukwikara hamwɨmwɨ nawe kemerano.  
\v 18 Nangʉ mwihaanɨ umwʉyʉ kʉmangʼana gayo. 
\c 5  
\s1 Twikonze urusikʉ rwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu 
\p  
\v 1 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, ɨtakwenderwa tʉbhaandɨkɨrɨ igʉrʉ wa ribhaga na amabhaga gu ukuuza Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu.  
\v 2 Imwɨ mwɨzɨ urusikʉ ryu ukuuza kʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ, rʉrabha rwa kuhwarukija nchu umwibhi chɨmbu ahaaza ubhutikʉ.  
\v 3 Hanʉ abhaatʉ bhakubhuga, “Tono omorembe, na tʉrɨ bhwaheene,” hayo neho ʉbhʉsarya bhukubhiizɨra. Ʉbhʉsarya bhuyo bhʉrabhahwarukija nchʉ ʉbhʉsʉngʉ bhu ukwibhʉra, chɨmbu bhʉhaazaku ʉmʉkari wʉnʉ akwenda kwibhʉra. Mʉgayo bhatakʉsabhurwa nʉʉrʉ hasuuhu. 
\p  
\v 4 Nawe imwɨ, abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, urusikʉ ruyo rʉtakʉbhahwarukija nchu umwibhi, kʉ kʉbha imwɨ mʉtarɨ mukiirimya ncha abhandɨ.  
\v 5 Imwɨ bhʉʉsi, nɨ‑bhaana bhu ubhwɨrʉ, na bhu umwise. Itwʉsi tʉtarɨ abhaatʉ bhu ubhutikʉ hamwɨ bha mukiirimya.  
\v 6 Nangʉ, tutigɨ kʉbha ncha abhandɨ bhanʉ bhakuhindɨra zendooro, toreenderwa totengeeze na kʉbha ne ekerengo.  
\v 7 Abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakuhindɨra zendooro, bhahaahindɨra ubhutikʉ. Na abhanywi bha amarwa bhahaanywa ubhutikʉ. 
\p  
\v 8 Nawe kʉ kʉbha itwɨ, nɨ‑bhaatʉ bhu ubhwɨrʉ, tʉbhɨ ne ekerengo. Tʉbhɨ nu ubhwisirirya nʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi, ebhyo bhɨrabha nchi ingubha kukikubha. Kwikɨ twisege Mungu kʉtʉsabhʉra, neho tʉkʉbha kina twibhʉhirɨ ɨngʉhiira yi ichʉma kumutwɨ.  
\v 9 Mungu atatʉrʉbhwɨrɨ korereke aturichɨ kubhwigatani bhwazɨ, nawe akatorobhora korereke tobhone ubhutuuribhwa kʉnzɨra yʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 10 Wuyo newe akuurɨ igʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ, korereke twikarɨ hamwɨmwɨ nawe, tʉbhɨ tukuurɨ hamwɨ turiigwa.  
\v 11 Nangʉ, mwihaanɨ umwʉyʉ na kwikongʼya imyʉyʉ chɨmbu mʉraakore. 
\s1 Eteemwa yɨnʉ ikwenderwa kubhiisirirya 
\p  
\v 12 Nangʉ abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, tʉrabhasabha mʉbhasʉʉkɨ bhanʉ bhakohocha emeremo ja Mungu gatɨ waanyu, na kʉbhakangata kʉ ʉbhʉnaja bhwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu na kubhiisasaama.  
\v 13 Mʉbhasʉʉkɨ bhʉkʉngʼu na kʉbhasɨɨga kʉrɨngʼaana ne emeremo jabhʉ. Na imubheene kobheene mʉbhɨ muriikara komorembe. 
\p  
\v 14 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, tʉrabhiisasaama, mʉbhɨ mʉrabhahama abhatʉbhu na kʉbhakongʼya bhanʉ bhakuurɨ imyʉyʉ. Na mʉbhahɨ abhanyʉʉhɨrɨru amanaga nu ukwigumirirya abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi.  
\v 15 Morore, ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉwʉʉsi atagarukirya ʉmʉkɨndichazɨ ʉbhʉbhɨ kʉbhʉbhɨ. Nawe ibhaga ryʉsi mʉbhɨ muriikorera amazʉmu imubheene na kʉbhakorera abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi.  
\v 16 Mʉbhɨ no obhozomerwa ibhaga ryʉsi,  
\v 17 na mʉtaniha kʉsabha.  
\v 18 Mʉbhɨ mʉrakumya Mungu kwa gʉʉsi, kʉ kʉbha gayo nego ewe akwenda mʉbhɨ mʉrakora chɨmbu Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ atwɨrɨkiryɨ. 
\p  
\v 19 Mʉtaanga Ekoro Ɨndɨndu.  
\v 20 Na mʉtasiihya ʉbhʉrʉʉti,  
\v 21 nawe mʉgageme amangʼana gʉ ʉbhʉrʉʉti na kugwata amazʉmu.  
\v 22 Mwirigɨ kʉmabhɨ gʉʉsi. 
\p  
\v 23 Mungu umwene wʉnʉ akotoha omorembe, abhabhɨngukyɨ imwɨ kwa gʉʉsi. Ewe ariibhɨ imyʉyʉ janyu, ʉbhʉhʉru bhwanyu, nɨ ɨmɨbhɨrɨ janyu, korereke mʉbhɨ mʉtaana kuririirirwa kuhikɨra hanʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ akuuza.  
\v 24 Mungu umwene wʉnʉ akʉbhabhɨrɨkɨra, arabhakorera gayo, kʉ kʉbha ewe ne‑moronge. 
\s1 Amangʼana gʉ ʉkʉraga 
\p  
\v 25 Abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, itwʉsi mʉtʉsabhɨrɨ kwa Mungu.  
\v 26 Mʉbhakeerye abhiisirirya bhʉʉsi kʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwa Kiriisitʉ.  
\v 27 Nɨrabhiirahirya kʉbhʉnaja bhwʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ Yɨɨsu kʉbha, abhiisirirya bhʉʉsi bhasomerwe ɨnyarʉbha yɨnʉ. 
\p  
\v 28 Ɨbhɨgʉngi bhyʉ Ʉmʉkʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ, bhɨbhɨ hamwɨmwɨ na niimwɨ bhʉʉsi.